{"tid":2055610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"七一慶祝活動集思 - 雙向行街","createTime":"2020-06-08T05:53:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T05:55:39.000Z","uid":281193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c06a01cfc39c98276b07554b84ec3b32d16707a9","tid":2055610,"uid":281193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T05:53:41.000Z","msg":"首先，我地想做出咩野嘅畫面？<br />\n<br />\n因應最近各地都有示威，各國領袖普遍都唔會想見到烽煙四起嘅畫面，所以都應該係打和理非牌。<br />\n<br />\n我地要製造一個百萬人上慶回歸嘅場面，最好多D英文標語，用英文宣讀一D宣言，以向國際展示香港人爭取自由，反對惡法嘅決心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問題係狗狗一定唔批不反，民陣亦可能會忌憚而未必敢搞。就算有不反，或者有不反而照行，未行到soogoo 就出放題，然後咬百幾個路人，唔使一陣就搞散個活動。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，由維記行到去Centraall嘅傳統路線唔係太可行，已經冇得搞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n倒不如試下雙向行街，<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>由鯽魚衝至西還，由各參與者自行決定起點同終點出嚟行街，按行車線方向流水，而避免自己人塞自己人。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n你可以由HKU 行去Wanchchai 買支可樂，我亦可以由nordpoint 行去sheuungwwan 買個杯麵，總之人人出街消費慶蛔龜，刺激經濟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住記住個目標係：製造百萬人上街慶回歸嘅場面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，西區一段可以考慮行堅島，而唔行電車路，<br />\n一來因為半山未食過放題，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二來横街窄巷較多，容易疏散。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三來可以由堅島行落centraall 可以經過美領使，响果度讀下感謝宣言。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3725034da74caf0c4edf125cd3c56afbd31f6bfa","tid":2055610,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T05:55:39.000Z","msg":"［行動post] 推爆佢 明天6月9日抗爭一週年<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2055589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2055589</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}